WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.000
ARE THOSE FIREWORKS?

00:03.000 --> 00:07.000
WHAT IS THAT?

00:07.000 --> 00:08.000
ALIENS?

00:08.000 --> 00:09.000
