00:22.000 --> 00:23.000
DIGGING AND FIGURE OUT WHAT

00:23.000 --> 00:24.000
THAT IS.

00:24.000 --> 00:25.000
BACK IN A MOMENT.

00:25.000 --> 00:27.000
ARE WE ROLLING ON THAT?

00:27.000 --> 00:28.000
WHAT DO YOU THINK THAT WAS?

00:28.000 --> 00:30.000
WHAT DO YOU THINK THAT WAS?

00:30.000 --> 00:31.000
WHAT'S THAT?

